0example netlist    
0****   input listing                 temperature =   27.000 deg c
 v1 1 0 dc 15    
 r1 1 0 2.2k     
 r2 1 2 3.3k     
 r3 2 0 150      
 .end    
*****10/10/99 *********  spice 2g.6  3/15/83 ******07:32:42******
0example netlist   
0****   small signal bias solution     temperature =   27.000 deg c
  node   voltage     node   voltage
 (  1)   15.0000    (  2)    0.6522
     voltage source currents
     name       current
     v1       -1.117E-02
